Annotation Type Pokemon


  • @Documented
@Retention(value=SOURCE)
@Target(value=PARAMETER)
public @interface Pokemon

    Documentation annotation telling others, we just want to catch them all.

    Example usage: java try { throw new Exception("YOLO"); } catch (@Pokemon Exception e) { System.out.println("We caught them all!!! " + e.getMessage()); }
